metadata.name: Confluence
metadata.description: This piece explores the intersection of technology and the natural world. The figure depicted embodies the idea of fluidity and adaptability, reflecting the constant evolution of our modern society. The use of organic forms serves as a reminder of the delicate balance between progress and preservation. The image captures a moment of contemplation, inviting the viewer to question their own relationship with technology and the environment. It is a commentary on the human condition, and our place in the world we have created.
